name: Jordan Feldstein
summary: Jordan Feldstein. Additional Crew: Live in Brazil. Jordan Feldstein was born on 12 December 1977 in Los Angeles, California, USA. He is known for Live in Brazil (2010). He was previously married to Francesca Eastwood. He died on 22 December 2017 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
